Usage:\
There are 3 main steps:\
1: Create a Stage subclass (see tutorial 1 for more details).  \
2: Add your new script to the main camera.  See tutorial 8 if you are using Cinch for 2D UI over a 3D game.\
3: Do setup stuff in your script's OnAwake() (see tutorial 1), and add Sprites to the stage (see tutorial 3) \
\
There is a lot more info in the tutorials.  Also, we're adding new tutorials and demos all the time, so check out pixelheavyindustries.com/Cinch2D/ for new stuff.}